Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of codes with statistical constraints to reproduce grayscale pictures using halftone technique, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the use of correction trees, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also touches upon error correction (cs.CR) and rate distortion problem (cs.LG).
